ctor Bundle, designed for beginners and seasoned gold hunters alike. This compact, powerful set combines precision digging with efficient sand sifting to make every prospecting adventure more productive.<br><br>The 13\" Gold Rush Prospector’s Digger Trowel is built for performance: heat-treated carbon steel with a double serrated edge cuts through soil, gravel, and roots with ease. The ergonomic grip with a 5\" handle ensures comfortable use for hours, and the included nylon sheath keeps your trowel protected and portable.<br><br>Paired with the 8.5\" Large Plastic Sand Scoop, this set lets you quickly collect and sift through river sand or paydirt. Featuring 78 holes per scoop for rapid drainage, a 3-quart capacity, and ultra-lightweight single-piece construction, it’s easy to handle even in tight spaces. Its durable plastic design and bright green color make it both practical and easy to spot outdoors.<br><br compact,=\"\" lightweight,=\"\" and=\"\" ready=\"\" for=\"\" adventure,=\"\" this=\"\" bundle=\"\" is=\"\" perfect=\"\" gold=\"\" panning,=\"\" rock=\"\" hounding,=\"\" beach=\"\" prospecting,=\"\" or=\"\" outdoor=\"\" exploration.=\"\" start=\"\" discovering=\"\" today=\"\" with=\"\" tools=\"\" designed=\"\" to=\"\" last=\"\" built=\"\" perform.<=\"\" p=\"\">\n                </p><div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n                    <div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-100\">\n                        <p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n                        <p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n                        <a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n                        </a>\n          